Email Spam Detection System
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Overview
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This project implements an Email Spam Detection System using Machine Learning to classify messages as Spam or Not Spam. The system leverages Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques and a trained classification model, deployed through an interactive Streamlit web application for real-time prediction.

